We proposed two methods in order to perform a bias correction: correction based on coefficient rates (CBCR) and correction based on quantile mapping (CBQM), explained in the following:
Correction based on coefficient rates (CBCR) between simulated and measured monthly records of precipitation (Eq. 1). 1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
