				\begin{document}$${fr_{m} = ECDF_{is}^{ - 1} (ECDF_{rm} (\text{Re}_{m} ))}$$\end{document}frm=ECDFis-1(ECDFrm(Rem))where frm is the corrected projection, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
